: a free version and a paid &#8220;BeFunky Plus&#8221; plan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Package<\/th><th>Monthly Price<\/th><th>Annual Price<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Free<\/td><td>$0<\/td><td>$0<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>BeFunky Plus<\/td><td>$14.99\/month<\/td><td>$83.88 ($6.99\/mo)<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s a quick overview what you&#8217;ll get with each tier:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Free Package<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Basic photo editing tools<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Limited access to design templates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Limited photo effects and filters<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>BeFunky Plus Package<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Full access to all tools and features<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>AI-powered tools like Background Remover, Upscaling, and Batch Processing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Premium design templates and stock images<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Unlimited access to filters, effects, and fonts<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-pale-ocean-gradient-background has-background\"><strong>The free package is ideal for casual users<\/strong> who need basic editing tools, but it lacks advanced features like batch editing and AI tools. <strong>The BeFunky Plus package is great for professionals<\/strong> or anyone who needs powerful editing tools regularly. It offers more flexibility and creative options but may not be necessary if you only need simple edits.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Does BeFunky offer a free trial?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No, BeFunky does not offer a free trial, but it has a free version with basic features.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Does BeFunky offer money back guarantee?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>BeFunky doesn&#8217;t offer a money-back guarantee as per their <a href=\"https:\/\/www.befunky.com\/terms\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Terms of Use<\/a>. However, you can cancel your BeFunky Plus subscription anytime, and you will keep access to premium features until the end of the billing cycle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How does BeFunky work?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>BeFunky is an online tool that allows you to edit photos, create graphic designs, and make collages. You can <strong>use it directly from your web browser<\/strong> without downloading anything. Its tools are simple to use, making it accessible for all skill levels.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Go to<\/strong> the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.befunky.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BeFunky website<\/a>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sign in<\/strong> or create a free account.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Choose the type of project<\/strong> you want to create (Photo Editor, Collage Maker, or Graphic Designer).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Upload your photo<\/strong> or use stock images from BeFunky\u2019s library.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Use editing tools<\/strong> like crop, filters, or AI-powered tools like Background Remover.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Once you finish, <strong>save the image or share it<\/strong> directly on social media.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How easy is it to set up and use BeFunky?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To sign up with BeFunky, <a href=\"http:\/\/www.befunky.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">go to their website<\/a> and click on the &#8220;Get Started&#8221; button. You can create an account using <strong>your email or log in through your Google or Facebook account<\/strong>. After signing up, you can <strong>start using the basic features immediately<\/strong> or upgrade to the Plus plan for more tools.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>BeFunky\u2019s interface is <strong>clean and straightforward<\/strong>. All the main tools are clearly labeled and easy to find in the toolbar. Whether you&#8217;re editing a photo or making a collage, <strong>the drag-and-drop functionality makes the process simple<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure c